Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.96,0:02:37.96,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,姬说她想养
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.63,0:02:40.88,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,哇  太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.26,0:02:42.68,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,为啥你们俩这么高兴
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.22,0:02:45.56,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,因为  在姬去上学的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.56,0:02:47.18,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,您肯定会把狗带来这边的吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.47,0:02:49.89,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,独自守家什么的多可怜啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.98,0:02:52.10,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,确实如此
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.65,0:02:54.48,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,不如说是有环境养狗吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.27,0:02:57.86,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,要养的话  请负起责任来养
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.57,0:03:01.28,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,不要厌倦后就选择置之不理
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.95,0:03:02.66,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,一直养到最后
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.24,0:03:04.99,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,当然我是这么打算的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.16,0:03:10.91,kakushigoto in 3,,0,0,0,,{\fs50\bord3\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H040404&\frz311.7\move(1152,298,1236,150,0,5735)}周刊少年  漫画人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.16,0:03:10.91,kakushigoto tip,,0,0,0,,注：作者名源自漫画家江口寿史
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.16,0:03:10.91,kakushigoto in 3 - heng,,0,0,0,,{\bord3\shad3\c&H1200A9&\frz38.65\3c&HDDDCDF&\move(1168,698,1252,548,0,5735)}新连载!!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.16,0:03:10.91,kakushigoto in 3 - heng,,0,0,0,,{\bord2\shad4\c&HDDDCDF&\3c&H3E354F&\frz37.42\4c&H40354E&\move(1124,938,1210,788,0,5735)}「白色鳄鱼」
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.16,0:03:10.91,kakushigoto tip,,0,0,0,,注：白色鳄鱼本是流传在美国的一个都市传说又名「下水道的鳄鱼」  这儿是指江口寿史在漫画截稿日逼近时产生幻觉把白纸看成鳄鱼的捏他
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.16,0:03:10.91,kakushigoto in 3 - heng,,0,0,0,,{\bord2\fs52\shad1\c&H23DCE7&\3c&H2A445D&\frz39.45\move(1336,924,1414,774,0,5735)}第一回
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.16,0:03:10.91,kakushigoto in 3 - heng,,0,0,0,,{\bord2\fs35\frz39.26\c&H1328B8&\3c&H1CE1EA&\move(1350,784,1430,638,0,5735)}大容量
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.16,0:03:10.91,kakushigoto in 3 - heng,,0,0,0,,{\bord1\c&H7D2C44&\frz39.26\move(1430,834,1514,686,0,5735)}60{\fs40}P
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.45,0:03:10.54,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,总觉得  养狗和开新连载挺像的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.17,0:03:15.50,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,一开始挺好的  但要长久坚持就很难
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.63,0:03:17.05,kakushigoto in 6 - zong,,0,0,0,,{\bord2\fs45\frz270\pos(524,144)}多久才会恢复连载啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.38,0:03:19.30,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,以及  要让其结束更是难上加难
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.05,0:03:23.97,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,确实  一旦开始了就得照顾到最后
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.22,0:03:25.55,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,正因为如此我是这么想的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.35,0:03:29.85,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,在未完结的作品里  没有名作
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.56,0:03:35.02,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,不管人气有多高  半途而废的漫画不管哪个都是垃圾
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.44,0:03:36.48,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,说过头了吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.36,0:03:42.11,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,与之相比  我有着让五部连载作品完结了的傲人战绩
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.41,0:03:46.20,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,虽然在这之中有三个都是短命呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.24,0:03:47.87,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,别说啦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.95,0:03:53.21,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,「漫画家只能干十年左右」
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.08,0:03:56.38,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,「所以请尽可能地对他们好点」
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.25,0:03:58.50,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,啥玩意  这是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.09,0:04:01.01,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,漫画家的十诫  我试着做出来了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.09,0:04:03.68,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,「请给漫画家寄信」
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.47,0:04:07.10,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,「因为没有反馈而不安  他们会泪如雨下」
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.47,0:04:13.73,kakushigoto in 11,,0,0,0,,{\fs60\bord0\pos(646,14)}漫画家和读者的10个约定
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.47,0:04:13.73,kakushigoto in 11,,0,0,0,,{\fs55\bord6\pos(264,254)}1.  漫画家只能干十年左右。所以请尽可能地对他们好点。
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.47,0:04:13.73,kakushigoto in 11,,0,0,0,,{\fs55\bord6\pos(264,328)}2.  请不要跳着看漫画。光是这样就很感谢了。
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.47,0:04:13.73,kakushigoto in 11,,0,0,0,,{\fs55\bord6\pos(266,402)}3.  请耐心地追连载。
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.47,0:04:13.73,kakushigoto in 11,,0,0,0,,{\fs55\bord6\pos(264,476)}4.  请不要忘记漫画家也是人。
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.47,0:04:13.73,kakushigoto in 11,,0,0,0,,{\fs55\bord6\pos(266,548)}5.  突然改变漫画路线是有理由的。
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.47,0:04:13.73,kakushigoto in 11,,0,0,0,,{\fs55\bord6\pos(266,624)}6.  请给漫画家寄信。因为没有反馈而不安，他们会泪如雨下。
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.47,0:04:13.73,kakushigoto in 11,,0,0,0,,{\fs55\bord6\pos(268,694)}7.  请不要骂漫画家。大家都经不起骂。
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.47,0:04:13.73,kakushigoto in 11,,0,0,0,,{\fs55\bord6\pos(268,768)}8.  连载作品长篇化了也请读下去。
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.47,0:04:13.73,kakushigoto in 11,,0,0,0,,{\fs55\bord6\pos(264,838)}9.  你还有其他的漫画可以看，但我只能画这一个。
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.47,0:04:13.73,kakushigoto in 11,,0,0,0,,{\fs55\bord6\pos(246,918)}10.  请读到最终回。并且铭记它。
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.85,0:04:09.31,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,不妙  要哭了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.60,0:04:10.72,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,太单方面了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.31,0:04:12.81,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,所以老师  狗呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.06,0:04:15.77,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,怎  怎么办…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.74,0:04:24.24,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,后藤老师  您在休息么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.65,0:04:25.70,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,一子老师
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.57,0:04:28.33,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,您有在养狗么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.70,0:04:30.58,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,已经是条老狗了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.20,0:04:34.79,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我初中的时候  无论如何都想养就买来了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.50,0:04:38.42,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,因为一个人在家的时候很多
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.88,0:04:40.75,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,可以说我是被这孩子所拯救了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.30,0:04:43.17,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.22,0:04:46.80,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,姬也  没有兄弟姐妹
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.35,0:04:52.81,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,爸爸欢迎回来
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.89,0:04:57.81,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,姬  要负起责任来养哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.02,0:04:59.52,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,可以么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.40,0:05:02.57,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,要像对弟弟妹妹一样的爱护哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.36,0:05:06.57,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,最喜欢爸爸了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.12,0:05:12.95,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,这样啊  小姬想养狗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.41,0:05:13.91,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.29,0:05:16.08,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,会变得热闹起来呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.75,0:05:18.71,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,话说  这位是谁？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.71,0:05:21.42,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,是我弟弟
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.80,0:05:24.59,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,原来不是独生子女啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.17,0:05:27.13,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我有说过我是独生子女么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.80,0:05:33.01,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,最近  有传言说一子老师在和某人幽会
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.60,0:05:34.31,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,真假？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.64,0:05:35.18,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,真的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.60,0:05:37.85,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,终于有男朋友了？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.10,0:05:39.65,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,这件事有必要开个会呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.90,0:05:41.73,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,毕竟是一子老师…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.61,0:05:44.53,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,肯定是被人骗了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.24,0:05:46.70,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,侦探团出动了哟
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.69,0:05:49.57,kakushigoto in 10,,0,0,0,,{\fs70\bord2\move(1068,428,1068,664,2027,2236)}会议中
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.69,0:05:49.57,kakushigoto in 10 - zong,,0,0,0,,{\fs70\bord2\frz263.4\move(606,422,606,654,2027,2236)}目黑川  侦探事务所
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.15,0:05:49.20,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,是不是坏男人必须得调查下
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.03,0:05:52.91,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,传言说是在遛狗的途中幽会
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.16,0:05:54.20,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,那就是公园了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.45,0:05:55.54,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,走起
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.54,0:05:58.08,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,好可爱啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.71,0:06:01.21,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,小孩子大都喜欢狗呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.63,0:06:03.88,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,狗狗会教人各种各样的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.50,0:06:07.05,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,对于情操教育似乎也很好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.72,0:06:09.93,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,拜拜
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.51,0:06:14.81,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,那俩孩子  每次我遛狗都会过来摸摸狗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.06,0:06:17.14,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,那真是辛苦呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.27,0:06:18.94,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,等等哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.52,0:06:22.48,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,这么容易吸引小孩过来  不是很危险吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.19,0:06:24.23,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,是狗狗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.48,0:06:25.61,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,好可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.19,0:06:28.11,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,咦  是小姬的爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.32,0:06:30.45,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,穿得好像漫画家啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.61,0:06:32.49,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,小姬的爸爸是漫画家
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.66,0:06:34.49,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,小姬的爸爸是漫画家
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.70,0:06:37.20,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,暴露的可能性不是变高了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.41,0:06:37.87,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.58,0:06:41.08,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,老师  请听我一言
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.25,0:06:44.09,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,说曹操曹操到
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.55,0:06:46.88,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我看见了哦…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.46,0:06:49.17,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,这只狗狗是怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.30,0:06:50.93,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,好可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.76,0:06:55.81,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,{\an8}乖乖
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.68,0:06:59.14,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,咦  没和谁在一起么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.35,0:07:00.31,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我没看到
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.56,0:07:02.19,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,老师以外还有人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.27,0:07:06.78,kakushigoto in 3 - heng,,0,0,0,,{\fs70\pos(840,350)}养狗的家常便饭
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.44,0:07:06.78,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,遛狗时  人们眼中只有狗狗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.28,0:07:10.07,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,在旁边的人基本上就跟空气没区别
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.90,0:07:10.24,kakushigoto in 6 - zong,,0,0,0,,{\frz270\pos(1110,140)\c&H213859&}早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.74,0:07:13.78,kakushigoto in 6,,0,0,0,,{\c&H141A2B&\pos(808,68)}无视
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.61,0:07:13.66,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,饲主的面孔也不会被记住
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.12,0:07:16.16,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,虽然帮大忙了…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.99,0:07:18.29,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,但总感觉心情复杂
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.41,0:07:23.71,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,你好  关于募集领养这件事…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.04,0:07:32.80,kakushigoto in 6,,0,0,0,,{\bord5\c&HF0F6F7&\3c&HD4DD94&\frz328.5\frx24\fry10\org(1485.6,265.6)\pos(1313.6,264)}送狗崽
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.04,0:07:32.80,kakushigoto in 6,,0,0,0,,{\fs45\frz331.9\frx12\fry6\org(1434,516.8)\pos(920.8,562.4)}狗妈妈生了好多可爱的狗崽
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.04,0:07:32.80,kakushigoto in 6,,0,0,0,,{\bord1\fs40\frx8\fry2\c&H4D5D71&\pos(263.6,996)\org(978.8,1047.2)\frz331.5}能把小狗当成家庭成员好好对待的人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.04,0:07:32.80,kakushigoto in 6,,0,0,0,,{\bord1\fs40\frz330.5\frx8\fry2\c&H4D5D71&\org(1149.2,1233.2)\pos(434,1182)}请致电
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.38,0:07:28.34,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,对不起  全部都已经定下来了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.71,0:07:29.96,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,这样吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.30,0:07:32.59,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,没事  谢谢了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.64,0:07:37.10,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,稍微  放下心来了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.19,0:07:42.64,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,姬
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.60,0:07:45.15,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,怎么了  爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.81,0:07:46.86,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,你在做什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.44,0:07:49.03,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,这是遛狗的训练哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.53,0:07:51.86,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,为了不被狗狗拉着跑
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.45,0:07:55.57,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,不是为了不被狗狗拉着跑
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.12,0:07:58.54,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,更重要的是教会狗狗不要拉着人跑哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.41,0:08:00.12,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.91,0:08:03.12,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,话说刚刚有什么话想说吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.33,0:08:04.04,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,没…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.21,0:08:06.21,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,没事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.88,0:08:11.38,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,你  你们在干什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.80,0:08:14.38,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,肯定是在做迎接小狗的准备啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.72,0:08:15.64,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,不是  还没…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.68,0:08:17.51,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,不管什么事准备工作都很重要
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.81,0:08:20.10,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,什么时候会来呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.31,0:08:23.35,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,其  其实…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.77,0:08:27.98,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,大骗子
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.06,0:08:30.23,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,不是说好要养的么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.53,0:08:33.65,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,为啥你们会这么悲伤哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.40,0:08:36.36,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,特别是你  那个时候不是不在场吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.70,0:08:38.45,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,芥子是之后听到这件事的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.45,0:08:40.79,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,他是我们之中最期待的那个
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.08,0:08:45.00,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,连这些家伙都变成这样的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.25,0:08:50.67,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,结果到最后还是我们在照顾
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.21,0:08:54.05,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,丈夫去公司  孩子去学校
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.63,0:08:57.55,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,没个老婆在家的话是养不了狗的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.60,0:09:04.35,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.44,0:09:07.98,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,姬？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.11,0:09:09.73,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.65,0:09:11.52,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,欢迎回家
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.99,0:09:17.78,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,关于小狗  说是找到了新家
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.70,0:09:21.12,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,这样啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.95,0:09:25.00,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,周末去宠物店看看其他的小狗吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.16,0:09:25.75,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,不用了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.04,0:09:29.46,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,果然我们家养不了狗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.29,0:09:32.30,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,毕竟只有爸爸和我
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.84,0:09:35.05,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,在这家里养狗的话狗狗会很可怜
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.13,0:09:38.26,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,所以  这样反而更好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.89,0:09:40.47,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,姬…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.85,0:09:44.81,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,怎么可能…养不了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.31,0:09:47.14,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,即便是我们家也是可以养狗的！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.15,0:09:52.23,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我们也是能养狗的  普通家庭！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.57,0:09:57.61,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,又是你
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.45,0:10:03.54,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,这是第三代
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.41,0:10:08.04,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,难得都准备了  狗却不来
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.96,0:10:11.84,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,至少出于安慰  把这幅画装饰起来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.42,0:10:16.92,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,狗狗和…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.13,0:10:18.05,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,小姬？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.34,0:10:19.76,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,这幅画是怎么回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.34,0:10:23.81,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,在这之前我去镰仓放原稿的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.68,0:10:27.48,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,在仓库的角落找到了个铺满灰尘的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.48,0:10:30.94,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,老师也能画这种画啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.27,0:10:33.06,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,日本画吧  这是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.52,0:10:35.86,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,这笔触  好像在哪儿见过的…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.53,0:10:38.86,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,这是最近画的吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.03,0:10:41.70,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,署名日期写错了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.37,0:10:46.87,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,姬
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.83,0:10:48.58,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,爸爸？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.79,0:10:55.17,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,这孩子是怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.50,0:10:57.34,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,姬说养不了的话
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.59,0:10:58.63,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,那就爸爸一人来养咯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.13,0:11:01.09,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,不  不可能啦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.22,0:11:03.93,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,只让爸爸一个人养  我也来帮忙吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.35,0:11:05.72,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,该怎么办好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.89,0:11:08.64,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,是吧  第四代
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.18,0:11:09.93,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,第四代？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.44,0:11:18.86,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,姬  会感冒的上床和爸爸一起睡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.53,0:11:20.99,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我要在这儿和狗狗一起睡
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.86,0:11:23.45,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,狗狗也带回来了  好啦听话
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.16,0:11:25.58,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我睡觉翻身会打到人哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.62,0:11:36.34,kakushigoto in 11,,0,0,0,,{\fad(700,0)\bord0\fs60\pos(704,172)}爸爸与女儿的10个约定
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.37,0:11:31.96,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,「爸爸只能陪女儿一起睡到十岁左右」
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.96,0:11:36.00,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,「所以睡的时候请尽可能的黏着爸爸」
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.89,0:11:47.60,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,姬
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.06,0:11:52.02,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,爸爸…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.90,0:11:58.48,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,好可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.11,0:12:01.07,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,老师  这只小狗的名字叫什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.44,0:12:02.53,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我还没想好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.74,0:12:05.49,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,不快点给它取个名字也太可怜了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.57,0:12:06.99,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我来给它取名字吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.03,0:12:08.08,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,为什么你来取啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.33,0:12:08.95,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,话说回来
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.75,0:12:12.37,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,这幅画  是谁带到这里来的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.33,0:12:17.96,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,也没必要这么责备我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.50,0:12:19.59,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,真是乱搞
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.13,0:12:21.46,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,这不挺好的一幅画吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.84,0:12:23.47,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,姬画得这么可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.80,0:12:25.68,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,原来老师您也会画这样的画啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.39,0:12:29.14,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,这幅画中的少女并不是姬
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.72,0:12:31.56,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,诶  那是谁呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.81,0:12:38.06,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,这是  姬的妈妈小时候的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.44,0:12:42.15,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,画这幅画的人则是她的父亲
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.28,0:12:45.78,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,姬的妈妈小时候的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.16,0:12:47.20,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,真是一模一样
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.78,0:12:49.58,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,姬的爷爷…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.33,0:12:50.87,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,那不就是…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.04,0:12:53.79,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,然后  同在这幅画上的狗狗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.58,0:12:55.75,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,则是这家伙的祖先
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.50,0:12:57.50,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,从画上的狗狗数起来
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.50,0:12:58.50,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,它已经是第四代了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.54,0:13:01.92,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,母亲养的狗狗的子孙
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.30,0:13:04.38,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,历经千万山水来到了女儿的身旁
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.47,0:13:08.64,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,感觉就像是已注定好的家谱一样
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.93,0:13:09.97,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,虽然很不甘
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.31,0:13:11.35,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,但这的确是一幅不错的画
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.06,0:13:15.64,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,虽然作者就是个垃圾
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.31,0:13:16.64,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,你说对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.10,0:13:18.60,kakushigoto in 2,,0,0,0,,{\frz334\pos(1001.6,596.8)}母女的继承人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.23,0:13:22.32,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,家谱啊  漫画家之中好像也有这个
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.78,0:13:25.28,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,就像谁是谁的助手那样
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.95,0:13:26.99,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,要是在师傅手下干的时间长了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.99,0:13:28.78,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,自己的画就和师傅的有些像了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.07,0:13:32.62,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,所以也就能够知道这人是谁的助手
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.12,0:13:35.79,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,你看那不懂行的人又在胡说些什么了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.29,0:13:37.12,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,是的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.54,0:13:39.25,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,不就是这样的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.00,0:13:43.30,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,并不是助手的画像师傅的画
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.63,0:13:45.34,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,而是那是助手自己本身的画
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.67,0:13:46.92,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我根本听不懂你在说些什么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.38,0:13:50.39,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,你的意思是老师不画了全都助手画是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.80,0:13:51.60,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,并不是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.85,0:13:53.35,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,只是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.68,0:13:55.14,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,会有些「风格」上相像
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.60,0:13:56.06,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,风格？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.02,0:13:59.65,kakushigoto in 3,,0,0,0,,{\bord3\frz270\c&H1E1F23&\pos(272,142.4)}发色光泽
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.64,0:13:59.65,kakushigoto in 3,,0,0,0,,{\bord3\frz270\c&H1E1F23&\pos(622.4,144)}网点
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.27,0:13:59.65,kakushigoto in 3,,0,0,0,,{\bord3\frz270\c&H1E1F23&\pos(969.6,150.4)}效果线
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.89,0:13:59.65,kakushigoto in 3,,0,0,0,,{\bord3\frz270\c&H1E1F23&\pos(1358.4,153.6)}路人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.52,0:13:59.65,kakushigoto in 3,,0,0,0,,{\bord3\frz270\c&H1E1F23&\pos(1748.8,156.8)}背景
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.81,0:13:58.60,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,既然涉及到众多的工作
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.19,0:14:02.57,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,那么恐怕原稿的十分之七都出自于助手之手
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.40,0:14:04.78,kakushigoto in 5,,0,0,0,,{\bord4\fs45\c&H3FDBF4&\3c&H1E1F23&\pos(204.8,944)}助手画的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.44,0:14:04.78,kakushigoto in 5,,0,0,0,,{\fad(1300,0)\bord4\fs45\c&H3FDBF4&\3c&H1E1F23&\pos(878.4,945.6)}完成的原稿
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.40,0:14:04.78,kakushigoto in 5,,0,0,0,,{\bord4\fs45\c&H3FDBF4&\3c&H1E1F23&\pos(1512,940.8)}老师画的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.61,0:14:04.23,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,也就是说
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.61,0:14:06.36,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,如果按照自己工作时的画法画下去
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.69,0:14:08.86,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,自己的画风也会同化成那样
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.62,0:14:12.24,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,是…这样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.28,0:14:13.91,kakushigoto tip,,0,0,0,,{\an8}失望
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.74,0:14:13.83,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,看上去你很不情愿嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.99,0:14:15.16,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,没有  没这回事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.95,0:14:17.16,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,你也不用担心
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.96,0:14:20.67,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,也就是最开始相似  等过几年
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.96,0:14:24.96,kakushigoto in 3 - heng,,0,0,0,,{\shad4\c&H6C703D&\4c&HA8BA8A&\pos(446.4,49.6)}助手
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.58,0:14:24.96,kakushigoto in 6 - zong,,0,0,0,,{\fad(600,0)\frz270\c&H445168&\pos(633.6,526.4)}进步
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.96,0:14:24.96,kakushigoto in 3 - heng,,0,0,0,,{\shad4\c&H6C703D&\4c&HA8BA8A&\pos(1289.6,51.2)}老师
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.58,0:14:24.96,kakushigoto in 6 - zong,,0,0,0,,{\fad(600,0)\frz270\c&H4A5263&\pos(1340.8,529.6)}退步
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.67,0:14:24.96,kakushigoto in 6,,0,0,0,,{\c&H495C70&\frz308\pos(875.2,526.4)}不同水平
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.71,0:14:23.29,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,师傅的画就会变差
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.38,0:14:24.88,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,弟子的画就变好了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.34,0:14:26.42,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,对  对
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.71,0:14:27.92,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,你说谁会变差啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.05,0:14:29.43,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我说的…是一般论
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.63,0:14:31.89,kakushigoto in 6,,0,0,0,,{\bord5\c&HBAA78F&\3c&HCEF2F9&\pos(1356.8,582.4)}搬运{\c&HD0CAB9&}钢琴
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.22,0:14:34.35,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,这是…怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.18,0:14:37.14,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,感觉好厉害啊  爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.73,0:14:40.27,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,又是那家伙啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.11,0:14:43.36,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,这是怎么一回事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.07,0:14:46.32,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,那么大的东西对我们家里来说只是个麻烦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.07,0:14:48.99,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,那是和狗一对儿的遗产
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.36,0:14:50.24,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,遗产？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.11,0:14:53.49,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,她一定和她母亲同样拥有着才能
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.58,0:14:56.20,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,给她找个好老师
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.54,0:15:01.42,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,真是的  多管闲事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.09,0:15:12.89,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,好…可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.05,0:15:15.64,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,这人已经是畅销新人了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.01,0:15:17.47,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,这人好像曾是老师的助手
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.68,0:15:20.44,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,就那个JUMP的新人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.52,0:15:24.11,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,这人的画风不跟老师您一样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.85,0:15:24.44,kakushigoto in 3 - heng,,0,0,0,,{\bord3\c&H40494C&\3c&HC0DDD9&\frz15.39\pos(537.6,200)}人气{\bord3\c&HC1DEDA&\3c&H3F4A4D&}大爆炸
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.85,0:15:24.44,kakushigoto in 6,,0,0,0,,{\bord4\frz5.201\c&H434C4F&\3c&HC2DEDA&\pos(388.8,438.4)}充实海鲜
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.86,0:15:26.32,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,没印象啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.48,0:15:27.82,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,这好像还是他的真名
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.19,0:15:31.03,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,偶尔也会有不是我助手
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.40,0:15:34.07,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,但画风和我一样的新人出现
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.12,0:15:36.66,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,喜欢到了极点自然也就会像的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.62,0:15:40.20,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,但也没必要模仿老师您吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.66,0:15:41.91,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,这其中肯定有的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.17,0:15:43.25,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,就算不是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.88,0:15:44.71,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,在接受责编指导时
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.00,0:15:46.79,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,这些是最近的畅销作家的画 你就照着这个画吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.88,0:15:47.84,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,也会有责编这样对新人说
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.33,0:15:48.46,kakushigoto in 4,,0,0,0,,{\frz270\c&H797F8B&\pos(1816,99.2)}最近的流行趋势就是这种感觉的画
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.46,0:15:48.46,kakushigoto in 4,,0,0,0,,{\frz270\c&H797F8B&\pos(763.2,212.8)}好的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.05,0:15:51.05,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,畅销作家…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.01,0:15:58.81,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我原本也以为是从咱们这里出道的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.31,0:16:00.56,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,毕竟画风这么相似
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.64,0:16:02.89,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,也许当过一回这里的短期助手
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.31,0:16:05.31,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,短期…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.82,0:16:10.78,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,想不起来
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.36,0:16:13.86,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,哎呀
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.53,0:16:15.70,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,后藤老师
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.62,0:16:17.95,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,这就是上次您说的小狗吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.91,0:16:20.04,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,您怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.62,0:16:22.75,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,其实  突然…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.33,0:16:25.42,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,出现了个和自己特别像的人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.67,0:16:29.75,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,您…您有头绪吗  对方是什么人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.34,0:16:31.63,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,完全没有
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.30,0:16:33.01,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,难道是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.55,0:16:35.84,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,和我干过一次的人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.30,0:16:38.68,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,这这这…这样的话
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.68,0:16:41.31,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,名字可能不记得但至少长相是记得的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.14,0:16:42.77,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,长相吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.06,0:16:46.60,kakushigoto in 3 - heng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(440,500)\c&H4F5153&\frz39.91\pos(163.2,417.6)}原稿我已经确认完毕
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.06,0:16:46.60,kakushigoto in 3 - heng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(440,500)\c&H2B5035&\frz39.91\pos(816,403.2)}18页第三个格子的背景就拜托你了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.06,0:16:46.60,kakushigoto in 3 - heng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(440,500)\c&H4F5153&\frz39.91\pos(664,937.6)}我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.89,0:16:46.44,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,确实  现在都是网络社会
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.81,0:16:48.23,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,如果是宅在家里的网络助手的话
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.48,0:16:50.19,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,也会有不知道长相的这种情况发生
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.36,0:16:53.95,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,也许是在网上认识和我干过一次的人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.91,0:16:56.95,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我好受伤
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.16,0:17:00.28,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,为  为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.00,0:17:04.83,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,原来是说的助手的事情啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.12,0:17:06.29,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,那你以为是什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.79,0:17:07.46,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.50,0:17:12.63,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我想那人应该是喜欢老师的画才比较像的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.88,0:17:13.80,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,你也这么认为?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.22,0:17:17.09,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,不也有狗狗会和主人比较像的这种说法嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.55,0:17:18.34,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,但也有相反的情况
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.64,0:17:20.26,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,主人会和狗狗相像
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.60,0:17:21.47,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,太过于喜欢了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.10,0:17:24.18,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,到最后大家都会变得和自己喜欢的东西相似
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.39,0:17:29.48,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,可能我也会太过于喜欢石原里美最后…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.77,0:17:30.56,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,太过于喜欢…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.44,0:17:36.95,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,和喜欢的东西变得相似
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.41,0:17:40.32,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,爸爸  最喜欢你了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.49,0:17:44.00,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,姬也会变得像我一样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.79,0:17:50.79,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,先变得和爸爸一样吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.09,0:17:51.75,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,你指的是什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.00,0:17:54.92,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,老师  我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.42,0:17:58.55,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,果然他不是喜欢老师的作品才模仿的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.93,0:18:02.01,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我向集英社的熟人问过了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.47,0:18:05.81,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,说是提了要求说模仿后藤老师的画风
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.48,0:18:08.06,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,果然是接受了责编指导啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.48,0:18:10.52,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,不愧是JUMP  有眼光
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.06,0:18:15.28,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,并不是  好像本来说的是另外一个后藤老师
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.74,0:18:18.70,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,是那个卖得比较好的后藤老师啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.86,0:18:21.20,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,说是没有重画的时间了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.37,0:18:22.74,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,就这么刊登上去了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.28,0:18:24.20,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,更讽刺的是这作品
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.37,0:18:26.62,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,不知道为什么还挺受腐女喜欢的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.29,0:18:30.83,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,青出于蓝胜于蓝
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.96,0:18:32.00,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,才没有胜过
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.92,0:18:34.84,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,不过竟然受女生喜欢吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.25,0:18:37.05,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我看着好像和我的没什么差别
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.55,0:18:38.97,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,难道这其中有些微妙的区别吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.51,0:18:43.89,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,为什么您一脸坦然地开始参考那部作品啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.14,0:18:45.60,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,您没点职业尊严吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.97,0:18:47.10,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,这不常有的事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.81,0:18:50.10,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,作品动漫化后  觉得那样的角色更帅
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.39,0:18:52.10,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,于是就将原作画风偏向了动画
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.06,0:18:55.94,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,青出于蓝胜于蓝
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.07,0:18:57.65,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,蓝便把青抄个遍
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.44,0:19:01.24,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,从来们听说过这么恶心人的谚语
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.28,0:19:03.37,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,话说回来  十丸院
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.74,0:19:05.33,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我叫你找的新人助手你给我找来了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.70,0:19:06.99,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,得赶紧增加点人手了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.00,0:19:09.29,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,如果您不介意听的话
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.16,0:19:12.79,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我问了很多编辑
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.67,0:19:13.08,kakushigoto in 6 - zong,,0,0,0,,{\bord2\frz270\c&H4F5C6C&\3c&HEDEFEF&\pos(1332.8,216)}那个
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.42,0:19:16.30,kakushigoto in 6 - zong,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,200)\bord2\frz270\c&H4F5C6C&\3c&HEDEFEF&\pos(902.4,220.8)}那个
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.58,0:19:15.96,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,大家都说不想把自己手上未来可期的新人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.50,0:19:19.09,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,放到后藤老师您这里来
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.55,0:19:22.30,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,就因为害怕染上爱写黄段子这一原因吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.72,0:19:24.39,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,也有这个原因吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.01,0:19:29.10,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,但主要原因好像还是不想将新人放到出道几率比较低的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.52,0:19:32.40,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,还不是因为你们一直没出道
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.56,0:19:33.90,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,这怪我们吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.61,0:19:36.48,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,后藤工作室不像不二多工作室那样
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.82,0:19:40.07,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,有着代代相传辉煌的家谱
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.03,0:19:41.86,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,你们听好了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.49,0:19:46.03,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,所有人  给我半年之内出道
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.54,0:19:48.54,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,老师…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.66,0:19:51.71,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,果然还是算了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.25,0:19:55.00,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,能不能等我培养好有希望的新人之后你们再出道吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.33,0:19:58.84,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,但这又需要自己助手出道的成果
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.55,0:20:00.97,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,真是进退两难啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.47,0:20:04.47,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,就当是人气作家都是从我的工作室出来的不就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.14,0:20:06.60,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,您打算是虚报自己的漫画履历吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.43,0:20:11.14,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,就算是跟了个多好的师傅
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.43,0:20:13.35,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,能够出道与否还不是得靠自己
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.36,0:20:20.86,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我在上钢琴课
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.24,0:20:22.40,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,这…这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.11,0:20:25.03,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我介绍这个人来这里的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.28,0:20:25.87,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.20,0:20:27.49,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,你别看他虽然是这个样子
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.58,0:20:29.49,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,但是马莉欧先生他可是很有才能的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.83,0:20:32.62,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,居然夸赞我是这个样子  我真是高兴
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.04,0:20:34.37,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,这…这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.67,0:20:36.58,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我一天就学会了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.75,0:20:38.38,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,这个
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.88,0:20:39.75,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,会沾染上变态病毒的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.05,0:20:40.63,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,滚
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.18,0:20:48.30,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,果然得让姬跟个好老师
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.10,0:20:51.72,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,这是姬做的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.35,0:20:54.27,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,虽然是纳德拉小姐守着我做的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.81,0:20:56.40,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,但全都是我亲手做的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.40,0:21:00.40,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,真好吃…而且这味道很熟悉
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.78,0:21:01.86,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我都是按照菜谱上做的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.53,0:21:04.15,kakushigoto in 6,,0,0,0,,{\fs60\bord3\frz18.85\c&H54DDF6&\3c&H2263DA&\frx6\fry4\pos(1160,712)}菜谱
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.86,0:21:03.82,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,放在那个箱子里了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.36,0:21:10.03,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,这也是代代相传的家谱吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.91,0:21:11.83,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.70,0:21:12.91,kakushigoto in 6 - zong,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,0)\bord4\c&HE8C486&\3c&HA98545&\frz281.4\pos(1078.4,422.4)}泪目
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.24,0:21:14.25,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,那是  狗狗吃的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.71,0:21:24.76,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,小姬她没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.05,0:21:26.84,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,肯定没事的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.13,0:21:28.47,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,嘴上这么说
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.64,0:21:31.26,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,但提议一起悄悄跟着来的不就是雾子你吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.14,0:21:33.10,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,话是这么说…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.14,0:21:38.23,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,你们  一起约好来开同学聚会吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.31,0:21:41.27,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,那可得叫上我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.69,0:21:45.78,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,一…一子老师
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.82,0:21:48.24,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,您居…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.53,0:21:49.66,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,居然没穿运动衫
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.74,0:21:50.57,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,你们意外这个啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.70,0:21:56.04,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,好消息和坏消息各有一个
Comment: 0,0:00:01.00,0:00:01.00,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,——————ED——————
